These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: swimming, cricket, volleyball
1. Sport:cricket is on the right of Sport:volleyball##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far right##1
3. Sport:swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | volleyball | cricket | swimming |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: pomegranate, lettuce, strawberry
1. Food:lettuce is in an odd position##4
2. Food:pomegranate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pomegranate | strawberry | lettuce |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: traveling, gardening, reading
1. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:gardening is on the left or right of Hobby:reading##3
3. Hobby:reading is on the right of Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | traveling | gardening | reading |

 #################################
 
